channel.title: Help with silabs, not working
channel.description:
Hi everyone,
I recently made my own server and really want a silabs one but everyone time I type in http://client.silabsoft.org/ or http://silabsoft.org it comes up with this error:
Forbidden You don't have permission to access / on this server.
Additionally, a 403 Forbidden error was encountered while trying to use an ErrorDocument to handle the request.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Apache/1.3.37 Server at client.silabsoft.org Port 80
How can I fix this because I would ask this question on silabsoft forums but I can't go there either, same error.
Can anyone help? Thanks.
